sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HTTP as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
    participant GRPC as vllm-tgis-adapter<br/>gRPC 8033/TCP
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant Spyre as IBM Spyre Accelerator<br/>VFIO Passthrough

    Note over Client,Spyre: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)

    Client->>RBAC: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token (JWT)
    RBAC->>RBAC: Validate token,<br/>enforce RBAC policy
    RBAC->>HTTP: Forward to localhost:8000<br/>HTTP (no TLS, pre-authenticated)
    HTTP->>Engine: Python in-process call<br/>Tokenize + schedule
    Engine->>Spyre: Model inference<br/>VFIO device passthrough
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>HTTP: Generated tokens
    HTTP-->>RBAC: JSON response
    RBAC-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,Spyre: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS Protocol)

    Client->>RBAC: gRPC GenerationService.Generate<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    RBAC->>RBAC: Validate token,<br/>enforce RBAC policy
    RBAC->>GRPC: Forward to localhost:8033<br/>gRPC (no TLS, pre-authenticated)
    GRPC->>Engine: Python in-process call<br/>Tokenize + schedule
    Engine->>Spyre: Model inference<br/>VFIO device passthrough
    Spyre-->>Engine: Inference result
    Engine-->>GRPC: Generated tokens (TGIS response)
    GRPC-->>RBAC: gRPC response
    RBAC-->>Client: HTTPS response
